+-----------------------------------+
|       User Interacts with         |
|        JSP Frontend Page          |
+-----------------------------------+
                 |
                 v
+-----------------------------------+
| User Submits Form with Details    |
| (First Name, Last Name, Mobile    |
|  Number, Email, etc.)             |
+-----------------------------------+
                 |
                 v
+-----------------------------------+
| Spring Boot Controller            |
| (Handles Requests)                |
| - OTPController                   |
+-----------------------------------+
                 |
+----------------|------------------+
|                v                  |
| +-----------------------------------+
| | Generate OTP for Mobile & Email   |
| | (OTPService)                      |
| +-----------------------------------+
|                |
|                v
| +-----------------------------------+
| | Store OTPs in Session             |
| +-----------------------------------+
|                |
| +----------------|------------------+
| |                v                  |
| | +-----------------------------------+
| | | Send OTP to Mobile via SMS        |
| | | (Using OTPService's sendSMS method|
| | | - Not implemented in example)     |
| | +-----------------------------------+
| |                |
| |                v
| +-----------------------------------+
| | Send OTP to Email (SMTP)           |
| | (Using OTPService's sendEmail method)|
| +-----------------------------------+
|                |
|                v
| +-----------------------------------+
| | Return Response to User            |
| | - Display "OTP sent to mobile and  |
| |   email" message                   |
| +-----------------------------------+
|                |
|                v
| +-----------------------------------+
| | User Inputs OTPs (Mobile & Email)  |
| | and Submits Form Again             |
| +-----------------------------------+
|                |
|                v
| +-----------------------------------+
| | Spring Boot Controller             |
| | - OTPController                    |
| | - Verify OTPs                      |
| +-----------------------------------+
|                |
| +----------------|------------------+
| |                v                  |
| | +-----------------------------------+
| | | Match OTPs with Stored Values     |
| | | - Session OTPs                    |
| | +-----------------------------------+
|                |
| +----------------|------------------+
| |                v                  |
| | +-----------------------------------+
| | | If OTPs Match:                    |
| | | - Display "OTP verified successfully" |
| | +-----------------------------------+
| |                |
| |                v
| +-----------------------------------+
| | If OTPs Don't Match:                |
| | - Display "Invalid OTP"             |
| +-----------------------------------+
|                |
|                v
+-----------------------------------+
|       User Sees Result on         |
|        JSP Frontend Page          |
+-----------------------------------+
